    DSPOp -->|launches training| TrainingOp
    DSPOp -->|launches training| Trainer
    DSPOp -->|metadata storage| MySQL

    %% MLflow dependencies
    MLflow -->|metadata storage| PostgreSQL
    MLflow -->|artifact storage| S3

    %% Model Registry dependencies
    ModelReg -->|metadata storage| PostgreSQL

    %% Feast dependencies
    Feast -->|offline storage| PostgreSQL
    Feast -->|online storage| Redis

    %% Training Operator dependencies
    TrainingOp -->|gang scheduling| Volcano
    TrainingOp -->|model storage| S3
    TrainingOp -->|logs experiments| MLflow

    %% Trainer dependencies
    Trainer -->|distributed training| Argo
    Trainer -->|model storage| S3
    Trainer -->|model downloads| HuggingFace

    %% TrustyAI dependencies
    TrustyAI -->|monitors| KServe
    TrustyAI -->|inference logging| PostgreSQL

    %% Llama Stack dependencies
    LlamaStack -->|model downloads| HuggingFace

    %% Notebook Controller dependencies
    NotebookCtrl -->|calls| MLflow
    NotebookCtrl -->|calls| ModelReg
    NotebookCtrl -->|launches jobs| TrainingOp
    NotebookCtrl -->|launches jobs| Trainer
    NotebookCtrl -->|creates features| Feast

