    RHODS -->|deployed on| OpenShift
    RHODS -->|API operations| K8sAPI
    RHODS -->|user auth| OAuth
    RHODS -->|TLS certs| CertManager
    Dashboard -->|auth| OAuth
    NotebookCtrl -->|auth| OAuth
    MLflow -->|auth| OAuth

